pack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":23490,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/17\/hypocrisy-mosques-no-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":34238,"position":0},"title":"Abdullah on Hypocrisy: Time will come when mosques have no believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 17, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Khaythama reported: Abdullah ibn Amr, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cA time will come to people when they gather and pray in the mosques, yet there will not be a believer among them.\u201d Source: Kita\u0304b al-I\u0304ma\u0304n 97 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062b\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38315,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/07\/akhlaq-sabr-samahah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34238,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Best Muslims have good character, patience, tolerance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: It was said to the Prophet, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, whose Islam is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe patient and tolerant.\u201d It was said, \u201cWhich believers have the most complete faith?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThose with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Ima\u0304n li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 43 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/24\/urwah-no-iman-cannot-trust\/","url_meta":{"origin":34238,"position":2},"title":"Urwah on Trust: No faith for one who cannot be trusted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn 'Urwah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBe not deceived by the prayer of a man, nor by his fasting. Whoever wills can fast and whoever wills can pray, yet there is no religion for one who cannot be trusted.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li Ibn Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33505,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/15\/ibn-masud-quranic-amulet-makruh\/","url_meta":{"origin":34238,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Amulets: Disapproval of Quranic talismans, necklaces","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim al-Nakha\u2019i reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, disapproved of hanging anything from the Quran around the neck. Ibrahim said, \u201cThey disapproved of all types of amulets, whether it contained the Quran or not.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 23464 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u062e\u0639\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33256,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/abu-bakr-first-compile-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":34238,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Quran: Abu Bakr first to compile Quran into one book","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy on Abu Bakr. He was the first to compile the Quran between two covers.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 30229 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Battal \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5311,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/18\/desires-submit-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":34238,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Whims: None has perfect faith until his desires submit","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of you have faith until his desires comply with what I have brought.\" Source: al-Sunnah li-Ibn Abi\u0304 'A\u0304s\u0323im 15 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u06